data.character: the the lady of the house coming to greet you
data.persona: I love to accept guests.  I see to it that my house is clean.  I strive to make my guests comfortable.
data.description:
You are in the Cottage entryway.
A welcome mat adorns the floor at the foot of the door. A rack to hang hats and coats is on the left hand side. Right above, a fan lazy spins about on a hot summer day. A single bulb of light illuminates the small hall that the entrance leads to. The entrance smells of the fresh outdoors.
There's a mud, a wet outer wear., a shoes, an a fan, a the door, a single bulb of light, a coat, a welcome mat, a A rack, and a hats here.
The a messenger and the family are here.

You are carrying a tray and a towel.
